title: Ornette Coleman - Crisis (1972 quad mix 24/96 lossless 4.0 DVD-A
description:
Ornette Coleman - Crisis (1972 quad/surround mix 24/96 lossless 4.0 DVD-A)

24/96 4.0 lossless MLP (DVD-Audio).
16/48 4.0 DTS @ 1536kbps (DVD-Video) for compatibility with standard DVD players.

Converted from quad QS encoded vinyl using a SANSUI QS-D1000 VARIO MATRIX hardware decoder.


Note: This is a live performance recorded at New York University in New York City on March 22, 1969. It was released in 1972 on Impulse! Records in quad. Personnel include Don Cherry and Charlie Haden. The final track has quite a bit of noise that sounds like loud tape hiss. I made no attempt at removing this noise since it's also present on the CD release.
